name: Meltdown x Fight Fair! "BRAINFREEZE!" Bracelet
description:
Very limited "BRAINFREEZE!" Silicone Bracelets. They come in 2 sizes.

Maroon is Medium and Neon Green is Large.

Front of wristband says BRAINFREEZE!, and back of bracelet has the diamond logo.

The large bands are 8 3/8". The medium bands are 7 3/8"

Wristbands are made from 100% silicone, and are stronger and longer lasting than rubber bracelets.

Each band is limited to 5

name: I <3 Animals by Eric So
description: Eric So mini-plush! So cute!!!  Blind box “I Love Animals” series includes elephant, leopard, lion, mouse, tiger, wolf, cat & dog. White “Special Set” animals randomly inserted. Approx. 4” tall.

name: Pocket Stache
description: Like his father, this mini macho stache has a moustache all its own – though it’s merely stubble at this larval stage. And as legend tells, this stache’s stache has a stache, but it’s so small an electron microscope is needed to see the tiny follicles. One day all of these staches will grow full and bushy. Measures 6” wide. This item is manufactured.
